Name: Impossible Target
About the game: Impossible target is a challenging sci-fi version of operation. You guide your rocket to the red target on the map without exploding. This game offers extremely challenging levels. It will have you frustrated by level six. It was designed to be near impossible to beat. I can assure you though, that beating it is possible. 27 challenging levels! FREE DLC later on.
